<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ .Title }}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="report.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">mosdns / 端到端测试报告</div>
        <h1>服务 E2E 中文报告</h1>
        <p>完整配置真实启动，覆盖控制面接口、DNS 数据面、规则变更、生效路径、缓存命中和并发稳定性。</p>
      </div>
      <div id="hero-summary" class="hero-summary"></div>
    </header>

    <nav id="tab-nav" class="tab-nav">
      <button class="tab-button" data-tab="overview">测试总览</button>
      <button class="tab-button" data-tab="dns">DNS 断言</button>
      <button class="tab-button" data-tab="api">接口检查</button>
      <button class="tab-button" data-tab="performance">性能稳定性</button>
      <button class="tab-button" data-tab="cases">用例详情</button>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section id="tab-overview" class="tab-panel"></section>
      <section id="tab-dns" class="tab-panel"></section>
      <section id="tab-api" class="tab-panel"></section>
      <section id="tab-performance" class="tab-panel"></section>
      <section id="tab-cases" class="tab-panel"></section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <aside id="detail-drawer" class="drawer hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="drawer-mask" data-close-drawer="true"></div>
    <div class="drawer-panel">
      <div class="drawer-head">
        <div>
          <div id="drawer-kicker" class="drawer-kicker"></div>
          <h2 id="drawer-title">详情</h2>
        </div>
        <button id="drawer-close" class="drawer-close" type="button">关闭</button>
      </div>
      <div id="drawer-body" class="drawer-body"></div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <script id="report-data" type="application/json">{{ .ReportJSON }}</script>
  <script src="report_renderer.js"></script>
  <script src="report.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
